race.comment: ERIZA SPARKLES (2) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from five starts. Comes off a (29.17) win last time, scoring by 2.75 lengths in a NG over 520m at this track. Looks a key chance on best form. POWER AND GLORY (5) shapes well for this after a lightning last start success, getting around this track over 520m in 29.22. Top win latest and rates a key player again. ZIPPING ARIEL (8) hit the ground running off an inside draw last start and was never headed (29.44) at this track in a NG over 520m. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Must be included in calculations. MY BOY BINGO (3) recorded a one length win (29.33) in a NG last time at this track. Already a winner from this draw.
